description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 200, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [200 Votes, Top 5% Score]
